posting_body: ['Centrally located in East Austin, This apartments offers studio, one-, and two-bedroom apartment homes.', "Offering residents a walkable, bikeable, and commuter-friendly lifestyle within moments of Downtown and Austin's flourishing employment centers.", 'With modern finishes and all the amenities you could ask for, This is the perfect community for your new home.', 'Unique Features', '16th Floor Community Lounge', '17th-Floor Pool Deck with Jumbo Screen', '4th-Floor Pool Deck with Lounge Seating', 'Athletic Center and Indoor Basketball Court', 'Bike Storage', 'Conceirge', 'Covered Parking', 'Dog Spa with Resident Lounge', 'Full Size Washer/Dryer in Unit', 'Garage', 'High Speed Internet', 'Pool', 'Roller Shades', 'Two Finishes to Select From', 'Work from Home Stations with Podcast Studio', 'Call, Text Mike to schedule a showing!', "Not what you're looking for?", 'Let', 'me  find something perfect for you', 'Mike Gonzalez -Team Price Locator']
